txt.en: 'Look at all that stuff. None of it meat, but it would do in a pinch. These Hobbits eat anything. Get back to Gramsfoot, Uglash will be waiting.'

Fool Hobbits won't simply die in large numbers. No, these little foes are hardy and made so by their abundant consumption of food. The masters of Gramsfoot have a plan to weaken the foe and it involves their food supply.
